{"id": "28034", "post": "<div class=\"post-28034 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-amazon tag-azure tag-google tag-google-cloud tag-ibm tag-ibm-cloud tag-microsoft tag-salesforce\" id=\"post-28034\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/microsoft-azure-is-the-worlds-largest-cloud/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Microsoft Azure is the World\u2019s Largest Cloud</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/amazon/\" rel=\"tag\">amazon</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/azure/\" rel=\"tag\">azure</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/google/\" rel=\"tag\">google</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/google-cloud/\" rel=\"tag\">google cloud</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ibm/\" rel=\"tag\">ibm</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ibm-cloud/\" rel=\"tag\">ibm cloud</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/microsoft/\" rel=\"tag\">microsoft</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/salesforce/\" rel=\"tag\">salesforce</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> August 16, 2021 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-28036 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash.png\" alt=\"Cloud Cash\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cloud_cash-150x150.png 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">According to <a href=\"https://stockapps.com/blog/2021/07/21/top-5-cloud-vendors-hit-47-5b-in-quarterly-revenue-microsoft-and-amazon-generated-65-of-that-value/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"stackapps\">recent data</a>, Microsoft Azure is the world\u2019s largest public cloud with $17.7 billion in quarterly revenue.&nbsp; Amazon AWS trails not far behind at $13.3 billion.&nbsp; The top five (which also includes IBM, Salesforce, and Google Cloud) combined for $47.3 billion in sales.</p><p>Microsoft and Amazon together make up 65% of the field, with others substantially smaller.</p><p>Interestingly, despite being known as a \u201ccloud native\u201d company, Google has fallen further behind, selling only a quarter of cloud services that Microsoft does.</p><p>Microsoft Azure has taken an impressive lead in the industry.&nbsp; When Azure launched in 2008 (several months <em>after</em> Google Cloud), they initially followed a PaaS strategy that was poorly received.&nbsp; But after revamping their offerings, they\u2019ve zoomed past the original cloud innovator, Amazon, effectively leveraging the natural links between their datacenter and desktop products and the cloud.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-28035 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales.png\" alt=\"Cloud Sales\" width=\"600\" height=\"385\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales.png 600w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales-300x193.png 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales.png 600w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/2021q1_cloud_sales-300x193.png 300w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/cloudflare-complains-about-amazon-aws-egress-fees/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"cloudflare logo\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/cloudflare-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Cloudflare Complains About Amazon AWS Egress Fees</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/meme-monday-were-ibm/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Meme Monday: We're IBM\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/centos-cat-150x150.png.webp) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Meme Monday: We're IBM</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendboxtv-how-to-get-a-free-vps/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"LowEndBoxTV: How to Get a Free VPS\" style=\"bac